Class IPEndOfListOption

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Loggable

    public class IPEndOfListOption
extends IPSingleByteHeaderOption
    Represents an IP End of Options list Option (Option 0). Used to indicate that no more options follow. The Type field has the following value: Copy=0, Class=0, Option=0 
     +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
 |0|0 0|0 0 0 0 0|
 +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
    Author:
    Gregory Bumgardner (gbumgard)
